{"tid":1666275,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"WSJ分析火箭事件中既中國水軍力量，顯示絕大部分時間，可能有一半回覆都係來自三毛","createTime":"2019-10-21T02:23:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T19:39:47.000Z","uid":48083,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5f03efcb7561bbd11223f6d0f2a77e058330fb89","tid":1666275,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T02:23:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xc2A61W.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxc2A61W.png&h=aebc15a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://dailyshotbrief.com/the-daily-shot-brief-october-18th-2019-2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdailyshotbrief.com%2Fthe-daily-shot-brief-october-18th-2019-2%2F&d=IZFSAkWTwbXSesVVmoeERe6xA88r%2B4g6PmjrNIuMcHw%3D&h=5462709e\" target=\"_blank\">https://dailyshotbrief.com/the-daily-shot-brief-october-18th-2019-2/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除咗嗰經理啱啱寫野既幾日<br />\n大部分時間，一半以上既回覆都係來自少於12個followers既戶口<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原文：<br />\nHow One Tweet Turned Pro-China Trolls Against the NBA<br />\n<br />\n&lsquo;This wasn&rsquo;t primarily a bot swarm. It was a troll mob.&rsquo; After his tweet supporting Hong Kong&rsquo;s protesters, the Houston Rockets&rsquo; general manager was the subject of a pro-China campaign.<br />\n<br />\nBy Ben Cohen, Georgia Wells and Tom McGinty<br />\nOct. 16, 2019 11:15 am ET<br />\n<br />\nLeBron James wasn&rsquo;t the only Twitter user who thought Daryl Morey&rsquo;s tweet supporting Hong Kong&rsquo;s protesters was misinformed. There was a whole army of pro-China troll accounts that happened to agree.<br />\n<br />\nA review of nearly 170,000 tweets, plus analysis from expert information warfare researchers, shows that Morey was the target of what appears to be a coordinated harassment campaign after his tweet on Oct. 4 set off an international furor and threatened the NBA&rsquo;s future in the world&rsquo;s most populous country.<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\nTo Read the Full Story<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wsj.com/articles/how-one-tweet-turned-pro-china-trolls-against-the-nba-11571238943\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Fhow-one-tweet-turned-pro-china-trolls-against-the-nba-11571238943&d=IZFSAkWTwbXSesVVmoeERe6xA88r%2B4g6PmjrNIuMcHw%3D&h=caa74238\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.wsj.com/articles/how-one-tweet-turned-pro-china-trolls-against-the-nba-11571238943</a>"},{"pid":"d6843acf41762fd0ec7712f4f0d86ac5d7acf9b0","tid":1666275,"uid":82640,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T02:24:56.000Z","msg":"講真中共其中一樣德政就係束住啲狗唔好出黎吠<br />\n出得黎預咗係中共放嘅三毛或者機械人"},{"pid":"04b4ff916babc55b923b4b50789755b3acdeb27d","tid":1666275,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T02:27:04.000Z","msg":"呢個要推上twitter."},{"pid":"e8c7cb96e662cc6bb32b39267cc8b0302882e31a","tid":1666275,"uid":303462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T02:37:37.000Z","msg":"所以直接report 就得"},{"pid":"db6866679650619df677954b2677e4ff83eb499d","tid":1666275,"uid":16109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T03:26:29.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n今日香港，明日世界"},{"pid":"baa509a355e3a23981ac4a9266152b92be616906","tid":1666275,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T03:27:42.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"83d080dae724ffa7e0db7a6df5840b781c2771e3","tid":1666275,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T04:16:03.000Z","msg":"香港根本係俾美帝觀察緊支那五毛同假新聞手法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n台灣同美國大選就知乜事"},{"pid":"5a4b050016b49801c26866d72bbe15106b681db3","tid":1666275,"uid":127807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"83d080dae724ffa7e0db7a6df5840b781c2771e3","tid":1666275,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T04:16:03